{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "飘雪之夜的星龙树下第1话 星龙祭在即！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "就快到星龙祭了！正当圣城附近的镇上\\n为星龙祭做着紧锣密鼓的准备时，\\n所有相关物品都被魔兽抢走了。\\n王子向伤心的民众许诺会在圣城举办宴会，\\n并出发追赶逃走的魔兽。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "这是龙赐予人们的雪夜。\\n夜空中闪烁着璀璨的星光。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "群星啊，愿你光芒永驻。\\n奇迹之夜定将到来——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我回来了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊～屋里真暖和啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "辛苦你们出去买东西了。\\n雪下得大吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "已经积得很深了！不过，\\n镇上看起来闪闪发亮，可壮观了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "闪闪发亮？这是怎么回事？\\n该不会，是什么事件的前兆……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "才不是那种危险的事呢。\\n你想想，不是快到了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "闪闪发亮……快到了……\\n啊，是星龙祭！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "没错！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "星龙祭？那是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "咦，你不知道吗！？\\n星龙祭可好玩了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我记得，是伊莉雅教的节日吧。\\n不过我也不太了解……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我只记得那一天人类会热闹地庆祝，\\n可那是什么日子？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "对于龙和森隐族来说，\\n也许不是很熟悉吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所谓星龙祭，就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "为庆祝巫女伊莉雅的诞生，\\n诸龙齐心协力，\\n献上了满天繁星。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "因此，巫女伊莉雅的诞辰\\n就被称作“星龙之夜”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "然后，庆祝这一天的祭典，\\n也就被称作“星龙祭”了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "原来如此。那么，那一天要怎么过？\\n要做些开心的事来庆祝吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "是啊。比如说吃美味的大餐，\\n把树装饰成星龙树之类的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "还有在星龙树下\\n互赠礼物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "互赠礼物？\\n为什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "据说伊莉雅出生的时候，\\n有很多人送来了贺礼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "然后就演变成了\\n在这一天互赠礼物的习惯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "还能收到礼物吗！\\n只有人类有，太不公平了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "什么不公平……\\n你自己也参加不就行了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "可我们又没有这种文化啊。\\n也不知道该怎么做，要怎么参加。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是啊。我也觉得挺有趣，\\n但我们大概很难……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120035_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "看门人",
            "context": "抱歉打扰了！有紧急情况！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120035_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "看门人",
            "context": "刚才有位男子跑了过来！\\n说是镇上遭到了魔兽的袭击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶诶！？不好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位，我们去帮忙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊啊！？\\n镇上的光亮……都不见了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "受害情况好像不是很严重，\\n但装饰和礼物都消失了。这究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子1",
            "context": "东西是被魔兽抢走的。\\n跟星龙祭有关的东西，全都被……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子2",
            "context": "一大群魔兽攻了过来，\\n一转眼就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那群魔兽到底为什么\\n要抢走星龙祭的装饰……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊！\\n星龙树没有了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "这也无可奈何。\\n没有伤亡已经不错了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "可这样就没法庆祝了……\\n我之前那么期待……哇啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "别哭了……你想庆祝的话，\\n就和我们一起吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "可是，要怎么庆祝……\\n东西都没有了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我准备在圣城举办\\n庆祝星龙祭的宴会。\\n我会邀请大家都来参加。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真的。我们会打倒魔兽，\\n夺回被它们抢走的装饰和礼物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且如果是在圣城里，\\n就算魔兽攻过来我们也能保护大家。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以，别再哭了。\\n开开心心地办一场宴会吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "嗯！\\n谢谢你，王子殿下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "要在城里开宴会吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。这样也可以和城里那些\\n不了解星龙祭的伙伴们一起庆祝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这也是为了我们？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是为了所有人。\\n我自己也很想庆祝啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "既然都决定了，就快点布置星龙树吧！\\n要弄一棵个大得不得了的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。不过首先要做的\\n是打倒袭击镇上的魔兽，\\n夺回装饰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "它们大概还没有跑远。\\n我们赶快追上去，好好教训一下它们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，各位，我们走！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "要夺回被抢走的装饰，\\n在城里布置星龙树！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20803_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}